title: Israeli forces kill seven Palestinian protesters on Gaza border - Gaza medics
text:
Israeli forces kill seven Palestinian protesters on Gaza border - Gaza medics 9:43am EDT - 01:01 
At least seven Palestinians were killed and hundreds injured by Israeli security forces confronting one of the largest Palestinian demonstrations along the Israel-Gaza border in recent years, Gaza medical officials said.   narration)
